title: Quinzena Religiosa
body:
It began its publication on January 1, 1901, and ceased on September 15, 1910, with 230 issues.

It reappeared in February 1911 and ceased in January 1912, with 24 issues.

1901: Year of the start of Quinzena Religiosa's publication
1910: Year in which Quinzena Religiosa ceased publication
1911: Year in which Quinzena Religiosa reappeared and ceased in 1912
